SetPenaltyRateConcreteUnitTest
├── When the caller is not the gauge stake manager
│   └── It should revert with {NA}
└── When the caller is the gauge stake manager
    ├── When the penalty rate exceeds the maximum
    │   └── It should revert with {MR}
    └── When the penalty rate does not exceed the maximum
        ├── It should set the penalty rate
        └── It should emit a {SetPenaltyRate} event
